            </meaning>
        </instruction>
        <instruction>
            <utterance>
                Toss with chicken, toasted almonds, and celery.
            </utterance>
            <meaning>
                (transfer-contents ?output-container-e ?rest-e ?output-ks-e ?ks-with-sauce-mixture ?sauce-mixture ?chopped-chicken ?quantity-e ?unit-e)
